oppgaver.hjelp_last_opp: Do you need help submitting information?
oppgaver.informasjon.modal.overskrift: Do you need help submitting information?
oppgaver.informasjon.modal.bolk1.avsnitt: If you have information on paper, you can scan the document and submit it digitally. By scanning the document, the image quality is better and it will be easier for your NAV office to read it.
With a scanner app, you can use the camera on your smartphone to scan the documents. You can combine several paper pages into one digital attachment, for example a lease agreement.

You can also take a photo of your paper document with your smartphone. You can attach the image file when you are submitting attachments from your device. If you are on a computer, you can send the photos to yourself via e-mail first, and then upload them to nav.no.
oppgaver.informasjon.modal.bolk2.avsnitt: If you are submitting information from a website, we recommend downloading the page content, if possible. Your tax return, letters from the Norwegian State Educational Loan Fund, and bank statements from some banks, for example, are available for download as a PDF. We do not recommend taking a photo of your computer screen with a camera.
oppgaver.informasjon.modal.bolk3.tittel: Make sure that the information you send is readable
oppgaver.informasjon.modal.bolk3.avsnitt: Before uploading, check to make sure the information is complete and readable on screen. If it is difficult to read the information, you may be asked to re-submit it.
oppgaver.informasjon.modal.bolk4.avsnitt: If you are having trouble submitting an attachment, make sure:
oppgaver.informasjon.modal.bolk4.liste1: the file is smaller than 10 MB
oppgaver.informasjon.modal.bolk4.liste2: the file type is PDF, JPEG or PNG
oppgaver.informasjon.modal.bolk4.liste3: the file name only contains letters and numbers
